2 drops:
• You're right, Blood Funnel is great here and also hilarious.
• On the other hand, [[Chill]] seems like it's going to gather more hate than solve more problems. I'd consider [[Standstill]] instead, maybe? You might be casting too many things for that, though.
• [[Sunken Field]] instead of [[Delay]], maybe?
• Love [[Oath of Lieges]] here, that card is way underplayed.
• It's... good to know that [[Overburden]] is nontoken!
• I'm... not crazy about [[Righteous Aura]], but it might also be fine? I think I'd have to play with it.
• Love [[Brave the Sands]], not so crazy about [[Serra's Blessing]].
• I get why people like it, but I really don't think [[Tale's End]] is good.
• I really think I'd go [[Sword of the Animist]] over [[Thaumatic Compass]] here.
• No [[Baleful Strix]]? I get that you can't really recur it much, but the Deathtouch is still pretty huge.
• [[Darksteel Mutation]]?
• You play enough prevention and make enough tokens that it seems like [[Luminarch Ascension]] would be pretty great here.
If you're leaning away from Equipment because of [[Suppression Field]], that does make a lot of sense.
